Sí.

00:12:30.846 --> 00:12:31.606
¿Qué pasa?

00:12:32.326 --> 00:12:32.925
Mi Señor.

00:12:33.645 --> 00:12:34.486
Es Mu Zhuohua

00:12:34.486 --> 00:12:35.565
culpable de algo?

00:12:38.805 --> 00:12:41.006
